Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/30/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the Biggie Smalls verdict, the R. Kelly verdict, and much more!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
